textBeforeTable: Requirements for Keep Upgrade and Power Boost (Levitation Lev.0) The Water Dragon of your Outpost is unmatched, Powerful, swift, and loyal.Citizens travel from the City to behold the amazing sight of one of the mightiest Water Dragons ever hatched. 10 The Outpost's Water Dragon is a force to be reckoned with. He is as mighty as any Great Dragon, perhaps more. The Outpost and its production is well kept. 2,066 Defensive Strength. 9 The Water Dragon now reigns as a mighty defender over the outpost, strong and confident. Laborers of your Outpost look to the Dragon as a treasure. 1,717 Defensive Strength. 8 The juvenile Water Dragon is now a strong sentry within the Outpost. He has grown fiercely protective of his territory. 1,379 Defensive Strength. 7 This Water Dragon grows even larger and stronger as he matures. He is now able to patrol the skies of the city. 1,055 Defensive Strength. 6 The young Water Dragon is becoming swift and agile. He is now comfortable in and out of the water of his Keep. 747 Defensive Strength. 5 The little Dragon learns to become protective. He still mostly stays in his keep. 459 Defensive Strength. 4
